dc_description_s: This data represents roads for Waushara County, Wisconsin in 2019.[StreetMaster, is a linear feature class that contains the high-low, left-right attributes for addresses. This feature class is used for geocoding and is also used to support dispatching. This file contains the official street name and is used for most County Centerline application needs.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: https://waushara.maps.arcgis.com/home/index.html#
